channel.title: [317] Firstclickobject? Where do I find this?
channel.description:
I'm not using PI, it's my old source from like 2008 and I can't remember what it was. Anyway I don't have an actionhandler so where would I find the firstclickobject?
If you want to know why I need it, it's to make "Mine" mine the ore instead of "Prospect" in my mining code. Thank you
